// ── vDSP (Accelerate) eltwise FFI — Apple Silicon only ─────────────
// vDSP fused ops (svesq + vsmul + vmul, vvexpf, vvrecf, etc.) give an
// additional 1.5-2x on top of the tight scalar C loops above, but are
// macOS-only. On Linux the hxblas_* variants (portable C) are used
